1. Piecemaker
   The Piecemaker is an open source Flash ActionScript 3 image rotator.
   This plugin rotates entry images from zinnia blog
   1.1 Requirements
      django-cms
      sorl-thumbnail
      django-blog-zinnia
   1.2 Installation
      1.2.1 Add stalwart.piecemaker to your INSTALLED_APPS
      1.2.2 Run python manage.py syncdb
      1.2.3 Copy or link stalwart/piecemaker/media/ to you media directory
      1.2.4 Add this to your application urls
       url(r'^piecemaker_(?P<object_id>\d+).xml', 
            'stalwart.piecemaker.views.render_xml', name="piecemaker_xml"),

